at0006.1.description: Record the reasons, if the distance could not be completed or the test was terminated prematurely.
at0006.1.comment: Example reasons for non-completion include (but are not limited to), if the patient's disease has progressed or physical limitations prohibit him from completing the trial, indicate "Unable to complete trial due to physical limitations". at0008.1.description: Record any circumstances that you believe may have affected the patient's performance.
